text: Sayyeshaa Saigal, better known as Sayyeshaa, is an Indian actress who mainly appears in South Indian film industry. Sayyeshaa made her acting debut in the industry in 2015 with the action telugu film Akhil: The Power of Jua. Subsequently, she was seen in the Ajay Devgan-starrer Shivaay (2016), which made her Bollywood debut. == Sources == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors Category:Actors from Mumbai
